"intro"	"phone_screen"	""	"descriptive"	"Hello______! My name is _________________________ and I am calling from the UCSF Osher Center for Integrative Medicine. I have you scheduled for a phone screening at this time for the MYP study. Is this still a good time for you?\n\nYES/NO --> reschedule if \"NO\"\n\nDo you have any questions about the study before we begin?\n\nIf YES --> go over study information\nIf NO --> go to legal rights\n\n"	""	""	""			""	""	""	""		""		""
"informationaboutstudy"	"phone_screen"	""	"descriptive"	"OPTIONAL:\n\nCPRS Reference / Research Information: \n\nDr. Wolf Mehling and his colleagues are conducting a research study to find out more about pain processing and pain management in individuals with chronic low back pain. We are using a variety of pain testing techniques including brain imaging. The study is being held at the UCSF Osher Center for Integrative Medicine and the San Francisco VA Medical Center. It involves a series of clinical assessments, procedures to determine your sensitivity to different temperatures, task performances inside an MRI, and smart phone texting. If you complete all of the procedures, you will receive up to $440.\n\nChronic pain is a common condition and is estimated to affect 100 million Americans. This study aims to further understand pain processing across individuals with and without pain and various physical and mental conditions using a variety of pain testing techniques. By taking pictures of your brain, researchers hope to eventually help identify biomarkers and develop more effective treatments for chronic pain.\n\nThe study includes up to 3 visits, which involve a series of clinical assessments, procedures to determine your sensitivity to different temperatures, task performances inside an MRI, and fNIRS imaging. \n\nDo you have any questions for me at this time?\n"	""	""	""			""	""	""	""		""		""
"legalrights"	"phone_screen"	"Before we begin collecting information, I am going to formally read you your legal rights, and if you consent, we will then continue to the questionnaire. "	"descriptive"	"During this interview, I will ask questions about your lifestyle, your physical and psychological health, including questions about alcohol and drug use, in order to determine if you are eligible for our study.  Once you complete this interview, our study team will review it to determine if you are eligible, and we can call you within two weeks of the interview to let you know of your eligibility if you request. Some of these questions are personal in nature and may cause you discomfort. This interview typically lasts 30-45 minutes but may take more or less time.   There is no cost or payment for participating in this initial phone interview/screen.  \n\nParticipating in this screening interview is voluntary. You may choose not to answer questions if you wish, and you can tell me to stop the interview at any time without any consequences. If it becomes clear during this interview that you are not eligible for this study, we will end the interview. If you have questions at any point during the interview, please feel free to ask.  \n\nThere is no direct benefit to you.  The information collected during this interview is used only for the purposes of eligibility screening and will not be shared with anyone outside the research team. The only exceptions to this are if you appear to be in danger of harming yourself or someone else, or if there is a report of elder or child abuse, at which point we may be required to contact local police to confirm your or another individuals' safety.  Information collected will be kept as confidential as possible, but complete confidentiality cannot be guaranteed. \n\nDo you have any questions at this time? \n\nIf you have questions about this study in the future, you can contact our Principle Investigator, Dr. Strigo. If you have questions or concerns about your rights as a research participant, you can call the UCSF Institutional Review Board at 415-476-1814.\n"	""	""	""			""	""	""	""		""		""
"participate"	"phone_screen"	""	"yesno"	"Do you agree to participate?"	""	""	""			""	""	""	""		""		""
"yesparticipate"	"phone_screen"	""	"yesno"	"Okay, thank you. If you do not qualify for this study, or choose not to participate, you may still be eligible to participate in other studies through our laboratory. Your decision whether or not to have your information stored for the purpose of contacting you about other studies in no way affects your eligibility for the current study. Would you like your information to be stored on a secure database so we may contact you in the event that you qualify for other studies within our laboratory?"	""	""	""			""	"[participate] = '1'"	""	""		""		""
"yes"	"phone_screen"	""	"descriptive"	"Great, we will make a note of that. Thanks."	""	""	""			""	"[yesparticipate] = '1' or [noparticipate] = '1'"	""	""		""		""
"no"	"phone_screen"	""	"descriptive"	"Okay, we will be sure to remove your information. Thank you for your time and interest in our studies. If you ever have any questions or think you might be interested in participating again, please don't hesitate to contact me."	""	""	""			""	"[yesparticipate] = '0' and [noparticipate] = '0'"	""	""		""		""
"noparticipate"	"phone_screen"	""	"yesno"	"Okay no problem. If you are interested, you may still be eligible to participate in other studies through our laboratory. Your decision whether or not to have your information stored for the purpose of contacting you about other studies in no way affects your eligibility for the current study if you change your mind about participation. Would you like your information to be stored on a secure database so we may contact you in the event that you qualify for other studies within our laboratory?"	""	""	""			""	"[participate] = '0'"	""	""		""		""
